entry.title: Castin' Craft Fastcast Urethane 32 Oz Kit 32032
entry.summary:
Vendor: Environmental Technology
Type: Fast Cast
Price: 19.65

Urethane Casting Resin -- Sets in 10 Minutes!

FastCast™ is a two-component clear urethane casting resin, which turns white once set. Easy to use, 1:1 ratio and is odorless.  Ideal for casting, quick prototyping, miniatures, models, taxidermy and more. FastCast™ sets to a hard cast in approximately 10 minutes at 70°F.  Once cured, FastCast can be drilled, sanded, shaped and painted.

 

FOR AIR SHIPMENTS, and including shipments to Alaska, Hawaii & Puerto Rico, this product is considered Hazardous.  Additional  HazMatFees Apply.  See Terms and Conditions.
